00:13:10.496 --> 00:13:11.936
He needs a snack.

00:13:11.840 --> 00:13:14.592
Whatever it is, Jesus knows.

00:13:14.720 --> 00:13:18.048
He is our great high priest. He is the advocate.

00:13:17.952 --> 00:13:22.368
at the right hand of the father for us. That's the ministry that he has. And so when you pray,

00:13:23.040 --> 00:13:28.640
You're actually being invited into the ministry of Jesus. And you go, Lord, I need help. And he goes, I know.

00:13:29.088 --> 00:13:31.936
I know exactly what you need. Thanks for asking.

00:13:31.680 --> 00:13:32.864
I've got you.

00:13:33.120 --> 00:13:37.600
And so here's where we're going to close. Hebrews chapter 4, verses 14 through 16.

00:13:37.280 --> 00:13:41.216
Seeing then that we have a great high priest who has passed

00:13:40.864 --> 00:13:43.712
Through the heavens, Jesus, the Son of God.

00:13:43.712 --> 00:13:45.952
11. Let us hold fast our confession.

00:13:46.144 --> 00:13:49.824
For we don't have a high priest who cannot sympathize with our weaknesses.

00:13:49.728 --> 00:13:52.864
But he was in all points tempted as we are.

00:13:52.832 --> 00:13:54.368
Yet without sin.

00:13:54.944 --> 00:13:58.848
So let us therefore come boldly to the throne of grace.

00:13:58.848 --> 00:14:02.944
That we may obtain mercy and find grace to help in our time of need.

00:14:03.328 --> 00:14:04.736
And our time of need.

00:14:04.704 --> 00:14:05.536
yeah.

00:14:05.408 --> 00:14:06.720
That's when we come.

00:14:06.688 --> 00:14:09.696
Just like Jairus, just like the woman with the issue of blood.

00:14:09.536 --> 00:14:12.160
We come to get help in our time of need.

00:14:11.968 --> 00:14:13.536
And we pray and we go,

00:14:13.504 --> 00:14:14.880
Jesus, would you help me?

00:14:15.040 --> 00:14:16.224
And he says, "Yeah

00:14:16.352 --> 00:14:21.152
I'll help you and it may not be in the time that you expect or in the way that you expect

00:14:20.896 --> 00:14:24.512
Because nobody expected him to worry about that girl's snack.

00:14:25.184 --> 00:14:26.464
But he cares.

00:14:26.624 --> 00:14:29.696
And he loves and he knows exactly what you need.

00:14:29.952 --> 00:14:31.776
And he is good.

00:14:31.584 --> 00:14:32.864
You can trust him.

00:14:32.896 --> 00:14:34.784
And so this week as you pray,

00:14:34.784 --> 00:14:37.216
Run to him, run to the throne of grace.

00:14:37.440 --> 00:14:40.896
And know that your prayers are being heard by a compassionate,

00:14:40.896 --> 00:14:41.792
King.

00:14:41.856 --> 00:14:43.328
Who cares for you?

00:14:43.328 --> 00:14:44.896
So let's pray to Him together.

00:14:45.920 --> 00:14:49.216
Heavenly Father, we come boldly to your throne of grace.

00:14:49.536 --> 00:14:51.392
To get help in our time of need.

00:14:52.320 --> 00:14:53.440
Jesus.

00:14:53.536 --> 00:14:56.448
Well, you're in need of a touch from you, Lord. Some of us need

00:14:56.704 --> 00:14:58.240
Some of us need hope.

00:14:58.368 --> 00:14:59.872
All of us need help.

00:15:00.448 --> 00:15:03.168
And Lord, we pray that you would show us.

00:15:03.584 --> 00:15:05.376
How to find that in you.

00:15:05.600 --> 00:15:08.544
Lord, that you would bring healing to us, that you would

00:15:08.352 --> 00:15:11.584
Reveal your way and your word to us, God.

00:15:11.872 --> 00:15:14.016
Whether it's sickness and death

00:15:14.080 --> 00:15:18.080
Or whether it's separation and anxiety, whether it's loneliness, or...

00:15:17.888 --> 00:15:20.640
Whatever it is that we're battling and fearing and facing.

00:15:20.768 --> 00:15:23.040
I pray that you would show yourself strong

00:15:22.720 --> 00:15:24.672
And teach us to trust you.

00:15:24.384 --> 00:15:26.240
Because you care for us.

00:15:26.080 --> 00:15:35.488
We love you, Jesus. We thank you that you sit on the right hand of the Father and that you are talking to your dad for us and that our name is on your lips. Lord, that's beautiful. We thank you.

00:15:35.232 --> 00:15:37.376
That you care for each one of us.

00:15:37.152 --> 00:15:39.264
And that you are saying, "Hey, Dad,

00:15:39.360 --> 00:15:40.704
Andrew needs help.

00:15:40.448 --> 00:15:41.824
John needs help.

00:15:42.240 --> 00:15:45.408
Mariah needs help. Lord, you are speaking that.

00:15:45.440 --> 00:15:49.248
right now over us. And we thank you for the help that we have in you.

00:15:49.376 --> 00:15:51.040
And we pray that today,

00:15:50.944 --> 00:15:54.592
We will be walking in faith, believing that you've got it.

00:15:54.624 --> 00:16:01.248
Lord, you've got every situation under control because you are sovereign. You are King of Kings and Lord of Lords, and we trust you.

00:16:01.056 --> 00:16:04.288
So we thank you, Jesus, and we pray all of this in your name.

00:16:04.416 --> 00:16:05.344
Amen.
